<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="lively-adj">lively <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'laɪvli/    美 /'laɪvli/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>活泼的；生气勃勃的；(思想) 活跃的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a lively boy 
活泼的男孩</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a lively discussion 
热烈的讨论</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a lively imagination 
丰富的想象力</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>(色彩) 鲜艳的；(描写等) 生动有趣的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a lively description of a basketball game 
对一场篮球赛的生动描述</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>The lessons given by Mr Smith are always <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (生动的) and interesting.  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. lively  </p></div>